{"id":1219,"date":"2023-02-08T17:58:48","date_gmt":"2023-02-08T22:58:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/?p=1219"},"modified":"2023-02-08T18:07:06","modified_gmt":"2023-02-08T23:07:06","slug":"part-one-for-forthcoming-book-on-uncertainty","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/part-one-for-forthcoming-book-on-uncertainty\/","title":{"rendered":"Part One of forthcoming book Posted on SSRN"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ive been hacking away &#8212; for way too long &#8212; on a new book, <em>Uncertainty, Justification, and Enterprise: Renewing Knights Abandoned Construct<\/em>. Im at least half a year behind schedule, but Part One is now <a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=4350162\">finally posted on SSRN.<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To celebrate I tried to get Dall-E-2 to generate a book cover.  I asked for &#8220;cover for a book on Uncertainty and Enterprise, possibly with a sketch of Frank Knight in the background. I got this rubbish<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-02-08-17.52.49-Book-cover-for-a-book-on-Uncertainty-and-Enterprise-possibly-with-a-sketch-of-Frank-Knight-in-the-backgroud1.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/DALL\u00b7E-2023-02-08-17.52.49-Book-cover-for-a-book-on-Uncertainty-and-Enterprise-possibly-with-a-sketch-of-Frank-Knight-in-the-backgroud1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1220\"\/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Source DALL E@ &#8220;cover for a book on Uncertainty and Enterprise, possibly with a sketch of Frank Knight in the background.&#8221;<br \/><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>I then asked for an image for Part One (Formidable Barriers, Forgotten Pathways). This was a little more plausible.  Still very much a work in progress Id say.  And I 